299
00:17:29.690 --> 00:17:31.890
Debo conseguir más malvaviscos.

300
00:17:39.890 --> 00:17:41.890
Lobo, lobo, lobo.

301
00:17:42.090 --> 00:17:43.590
Si, si, si.

302
00:18:03.190 --> 00:18:05.690
